text.header1: Tsegulani maulalo Motetezedwa komanso Mosadziwika pogwiritsa ntchito Kasm Open-in-Isolation.
text.header2: Kasm Open in Isolation msakatuli wowonjezera amapereka njira yodina kumanja kuti mutsegule maulalo awebusayiti mumsakatuli wotalikirana ndi Workspaces. Izi zimapangitsa kuti zikhale zosavuta komanso zosavuta kutsegula ma URL okayikitsa/osatetezeka kapena kusunga zinsinsi zanu. Popeza tsamba lawebusayiti limaperekedwa mkati mwa msakatuli wapamalo ogwirira ntchito, m'malo mogwiritsidwa ntchito pakompyuta yanu, mumatha kulumikizana ndi tsambali mosadziwika bwino.
text.header3: Onani zolemba za Kasm kuti mumve zambiri.

title.tooltip1: Go idzatsegula ulalo mu Workspace yatsopano, njira ya Cast Key ndi malo ogwirira ntchito omwe alipo
title.tooltip2: Mukatsegula zolemba mu gawo la Kasm Workspaces pokhapokha chingwecho chili ulalo wovomerezeka chidzaperekedwa ku injini yosakira.
title.tooltip3: Ngati mutsegula zolemba mu Workspace mungafune kusintha zingwe zomwe zadutsa ku Workspace (Pezani zothandizira RegExp yokhazikika yokhala ndi delimiters /regexp/g)
